blog.name: bakugoukatsukizine
blog.title: FROM THE GROUND UP
blog.description: E-Mail: bakugoukatsukizine@gmail.com // Pre-Orders CLOSED // Zines on their way!

summary: Update: March 7, 2019 We have received bubble mailers last Saturday! These boxes are some big boys! They're starting to flood...
body:
Update: March 7, 2019

We have received bubble mailers last Saturday! These boxes are some big boys! They’re starting to flood Mod Kiri’s room! We also received some mini poly bags to keep our buttons from jiggling about in the mail!

We nearly have everything but the wait is not over!  These are our last three items in production!

Our hardcopy proof of the zine has been ordered and shipped! We are waiting to get it in our hands for a quality check before being approved for final production! If we receive the hardcopy before Thursday, we may choose to update a little early!

The lanyard sample has been approved and the digital charm proof as well! We’ve paid extra shipping in order to have the charms and lanyards sent to us sooner! Both are in production!

We have another announcement to make!

As you know, we were unable to unlock our last two stretch goals. Because of the misfortune, we were not able to provide each to our buyers or reveal the designer. However, there is still a chance to get these items!

More will be disclosed about this opportunity in next weeks update!

As always, make sure to e-mail us at bakugoukatsukizine@gmail.com with any concerns! We surely appreciate all of the support you have given us!

Mod Baku & Mod Kiri
